						               													<description>A game about observation and speed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The deck contains some funny figures of simple men, each figure is divided in three parts: head, bust and legs. Each of these parts can have different shapes and color. For instance, we could have a men with a smiling head, a red bust and green-red legs. Another men could have a king head (with a crown), a green bust and some orange legs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Setup: draw seven card and place them in circle on the table,&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay: each turn a new card is draft from the deck. If the new card has two characteristcs matching at least two characteristcs of the cards already on the table (the seven cards) players must touch the matching card. The quickest player scores one point. If a player touches the wrong card, it loses 2 points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Win conditions: game ends when the deck is over. The player with the higher number of points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
